embeddedItem.name: Camo Paint
embeddedItem.desc: Upon use, enemies will be less likely to detect your team for <nobr>75</nobr>s.
embeddedItem.lore:
The mysterious liquid changes color based on the environment.
You'll do the same in a few years' time after graduation.

"You're a chameleon, Oswaldo. You know what I mean?"
"The IPC could use a few chameleons."

29328.name: Credit
29328.desc: This currency, used by the Interastral Peace Corporation to settle accounts with its customers, is now widely accepted as the hard currency for space travel.
29328.lore: "People run around fighting and trading for numbers in a terminal, but the truly precious cannot be bought."

273305.name: Recipe: Camo Paint
273305.desc: A simple equation. When entered into the Synthesizer, it will unlock a new recipe.

440416.name: Solid Water
440416.lore:
Compound composed of hydrogen and oxygen, essential to support carbon-based life.
Keeping it in the solid state makes it easy to carry.

"...Isn't it ice?"
"No, no, no. Ice is ice, this is water, just in the solid state."
"...Isn't that the definition of ice?"
comeFrom: Storage Zone: Baryons or other enemies
Found in destructible objects in Jarilo-VI

757744.name: Virtual Particle
757744.lore:
Tiny particles commonly found in the universe but cannot be observed in theory.
Scientists are good at transforming theories into reality.

"I've got a virtual particle and an anti virtual particle here. How do we turn them into a real particle and a real antiparticle? Now, look closely..."
comeFrom: Storage Zone: Baryons or other enemies
Found in destructible objects in the Herta Space Station
